<?xml-stylesheet type="text/xsl" media="screen" href="/~d/styles/rss2full.xsl"?><?xml-stylesheet type="text/css" media="screen" href="http://feeds.feedburner.com/~d/styles/itemcontent.css"?><rss xmlns:content="http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/content/" xmlns:wfw="http://wellformedweb.org/CommentAPI/" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/" xmlns:atom="http://www.w3.org/2005/Atom" xmlns:sy="http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/syndication/" xmlns:slash="http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/slash/" version="2.0"><channel><title>UNWIRE.HK</title><link>https://unwire.hk/</link><description /><lastBuildDate>Wed, 13 Jul 2022 11:44:58 +0000</lastBuildDate><language>zh-TW</language><sy:updatePeriod>hourly	</sy:updatePeriod><sy:updateFrequency>1	</sy:updateFrequency><atom10:link xmlns:atom10="http://www.w3.org/2005/Atom" rel="self" type="application/rss+xml" href="http://feeds.feedburner.com/unwirelife" /><feedburner:info xmlns:feedburner="http://rssnamespace.org/feedburner/ext/1.0" uri="unwirelife" /><atom10:link xmlns:atom10="http://www.w3.org/2005/Atom" rel="hub" href="http://pubsubhubbub.appspot.com/" /><item><title>九巴 App 新增小巴到站資訊，地圖查找專線小巴站 + 到站時間</title><link>https://unwire.hk/2022/07/13/klb-app/fun-tech/?utm_source=rss&amp;utm_medium=rss&amp;utm_campaign=klb-app</link><dc:creator><![CDATA[EMMA]]></dc:creator><pubDate>Wed, 13 Jul 2022 11:44:58 +0000</pubDate><category><![CDATA[科技趣聞]]></category><guid isPermaLink="false">https://unwire.hk/?p=1110316</guid><description><![CDATA[<p>除了運輸署的「香港出行易」應用程式可實時瞭解九巴及小巴到站資訊外，市民現亦可於最新版九巴 App「App 19 [&#8230;]</p></p>]]></description><content:encoded><![CDATA[<p>除了運輸署的「香港出行易」應用程式可實時瞭解九巴及小巴到站資訊外，市民現亦可於最新版九巴 App「App 1933-KMB．LWB」查看小巴路線資訊及預計到站時間。</p><p><img loading="lazy" class="alignnone size-medium wp-image-1110319 aligncenter" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/07/IMG_3589-431x580.jpg" alt="" width="431" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/07/IMG_3589-431x580.jpg 431w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/07/IMG_3589-668x900.jpg 668w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/07/IMG_3589-768x1034.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/07/IMG_3589.jpg 828w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 431px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">（圖片來源：<span class="s2">AppStore）</span></p><p>九巴近日釋出更新版「App 1933-KMB．LWB」，只要將應用程式更新至最新版 V.2.0.0，然後透過應用程式內的「搜尋」輸入將乘搭的小巴路線，頁面便會出現該路線選項讓乘客點擊，查看小巴的預計到站時間及該小巴站的確實位置。</p><p><img loading="lazy" class="size-medium wp-image-1110320 aligncenter" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/07/IMG_3585-281x580.jpg" alt="" width="281" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/07/IMG_3585-281x580.jpg 281w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/07/IMG_3585-435x900.jpg 435w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/07/IMG_3585-768x1588.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/07/IMG_3585-743x1536.jpg 743w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/07/IMG_3585.jpg 828w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 281px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" class="alignnone size-medium wp-image-1110322 aligncenter" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/07/IMG_3587-280x580.jpg" alt="" width="280" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/07/IMG_3587-280x580.jpg 280w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/07/IMG_3587-434x900.jpg 434w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/07/IMG_3587-768x1592.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/07/IMG_3587-741x1536.jpg 741w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/07/IMG_3587.jpg 828w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 280px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">（圖片來源：<span class="s2">九巴 App）</span></p><p>「App 1933-KMB．LWB」加強了路線搜尋介面，乘客輸入小巴路線後，「搜尋」介面會明確顯示該選項是查看小巴資訊，為免因小巴路線名稱與九巴或城巴的路線相同而出現誤會。</p><p class="p1"><span class="s1">資料</span><span class="s2">來源：九巴 App</span></p><p class="p2">—</p><p 