</div>]]></content:encoded></item><item><title>Apple 新 MagSafe 充電線獨立發售，採用 M2 MacBook Air 相同 4 色編織物料</title><link>https://unwire.hk/2022/07/13/4-magsafe-3-m2-macbook-air/fun-tech/?utm_source=rss&amp;utm_medium=rss&amp;utm_campaign=4-magsafe-3-m2-macbook-air</link><dc:creator><![CDATA[Christy]]></dc:creator><pubDate>Wed, 13 Jul 2022 11:33:01 +0000</pubDate><category><![CDATA[科技趣聞]]></category><category><![CDATA[M2 MacBook Air]]></category><category><![CDATA[MagSafe 3]]></category><guid isPermaLink="false">https://unwire.hk/?p=1110330</guid><description><![CDATA[<p>全新 M2 MacBook Air 在上週五（8 日）起開始接受預訂，近日 Apple 卻推出與 M2 Mac [&#8230;]</p></p>]]></description><content:encoded><![CDATA[<p style="font-weight: 400;">全新 M2 MacBook Air 在上週五（8 日）起開始接受預訂，近日 Apple 卻推出與 M2 MacBook Air 相同配色的 USB-C 轉 MagSafe 3 連接線。MagSafe 3 連接線與 M2 MacBook Air 一樣，有太空灰、銀色、午夜暗色、星光色共 4 色供買家選擇，定價為 349 港元。</p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/07/MPL23.jpeg"><img loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1110335" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/07/MPL23-580x580.jpeg" alt="" width="580" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/07/MPL23-580x580.jpeg 580w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/07/MPL23-900x900.jpeg 900w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/07/MPL23-120x120.jpeg 120w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/07/MPL23-768x768.jpeg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/07/MPL23.jpeg 1144w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 580px" /></a> <a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/07/MLYV3.jpeg"><img loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1110336" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/07/MLYV3-580x580.jpeg" alt="" width="580" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/07/MLYV3-580x580.jpeg 580w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/07/MLYV3-900x900.jpeg 900w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/07/MLYV3-120x120.jpeg 120w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/07/MLYV3-768x768.jpeg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/07/MLYV3.jpeg 1144w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 580px" /></a> <a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/07/MPL43.jpeg"><img loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1110337" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/07/MPL43-580x580.jpeg" alt="" width="580" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/07/MPL43-580x580.jpeg 580w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/07/MPL43-900x900.jpeg 900w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/07/MPL43-120x120.jpeg 120w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/07/MPL43-768x768.jpeg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/07/MPL43.jpeg 1144w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 580px" /></a> <a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/07/MPL33.jpeg"><img loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1110338" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/07/MPL33-580x580.jpeg" alt="" width="580" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/07/MPL33-580x580.jpeg 580w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/07/MPL33-900x900.jpeg 900w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/07/MPL33-120x120.jpeg 120w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/07/MPL33-768x768.jpeg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/07/MPL33.jpeg 1144w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 580px" /></a></p><p style="text-align: center;">圖片來源：Apple 香港官網</p><p style="font-weight: 400;">雖然購買 M2 MacBook Air 會依照買家選擇的機身顏色，跟機附送相應顏色的 MagSafe 3 連接線。但這款 MagSafe 3 連接線同樣支援去年推出家 14 及 16 吋 MacBook Pro，因此非 M2 MacBook Air 用家亦可選購。</p><p style="font-weight: 400;">這款連接線接頭利用 MagSafe 3 技術，讓線纜以磁性方式連接至 MacBook，能防止意外斷開連接。配合 USB-C 電源轉換器使用，便能為提電腦充電。MagSafe 3 連接線全長兩米，改用了編織設計，令連接線更持久耐用。</p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/07/截圖-2022-07-13-11.28.41.png"><img loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1110332" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/07/截圖-2022-07-13-11.28.41-694x538.png" alt="" width="694" height="538" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/07/截圖-2022-07-13-11.28.41-694x538.png 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/07/截圖-2022-07-13-11.28.41-1162x900.png 1162w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/07/截圖-2022-07-13-11.28.41-768x595.png 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/07/截圖-2022-07-13-11.28.41-1536x1190.png 1536w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/07/截圖-2022-07-13-11.28.41.png 1820w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a></p><p style="text-align: center;">圖片來源：Apple 香港官網</p><p style="font-weight: 400;">資料來源：Apple</p><p style="font-weight: 400;">—</p><p style="font-weight: 400;"><u>unwire.hk </u>Mewe 專頁 : <a href="https://mewe.com/p/unwirehk"><u>https://mewe.com/p/unwirehk</u></a></p><h2> 最新影片</h2><iframe style="display: block; margin: 0px auto;" id="_ytid_84661" width="590" height="332" data-origwidth="590" data-origheight="332" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/?enablejsapi=1&amp;list=PLiEPZioiGtHw9_9gm4Ty0_pTEviOKNvfl&amp;autoplay=0&amp;cc_load_policy=0&amp;cc_lang_pref=&amp;iv_load_policy=1&amp;loop=0&amp;modestbranding=1&amp;rel=0&amp;fs=1&amp;playsinline=1&amp;autohide=1&amp;theme=light&amp;color=white&amp;controls=0&amp;" class="__youtube_prefs__  epyt-is-override  no-lazyload" title="YouTube player" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture" allowfullscreen="" data-no-lazy="1" data-skipgform_ajax_framebjll=""></iframe></p><div class="feedflare">
