求他們到平壤接受密集數學訓練，並送到盟國中國、俄羅斯接受網路戰培訓，以從小為國家培養黑客。由於與中俄兩國與北韓為盟友，因此能監視黑客的一舉一動，要求他們每天早上 6 點起床，工作 16 小時。</p><blockquote class="twitter-tweet" data-width="500" data-dnt="true"><p lang="en" dir="ltr">Potential hackers are then sent to Russia &amp; China for specialized cyber warfare training.</p><p>Because these countries are allies, North Korea can easily surveillance them and prevent defections.</p><p>Hackers wake up at 6am, and work 16 hours a day. <a href="https://t.co/bOtCCdjR5D">pic.twitter.com/bOtCCdjR5D</a></p><p>&mdash; Edgy &#8211; The DeFi Edge 🗡️ (@thedefiedge) <a href="https://twitter.com/thedefiedge/status/1545093516920889346?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw">July 7, 2022</a></p></blockquote><p><script async src="https://platform.twitter.com/widgets.js" charset="utf-8"></script></p><p style="font-weight: 400;">Edgy 又表示，北韓黑客近期改以加密貨幣市場作重點，看準其利潤及可觀性，能透過 Tornado Cash 等混幣協議，令洗錢能較其他途徑容易。他指出「39 號室」今年發動涉及 6.25 億美元（約 49.06 億港元）和 1 億美元（約 7.85 億港元）的 Ronin 跨鏈橋攻擊及 Harmony 跨鏈橋攻擊。</p><p style="font-weight: 400;">資料來源：<a href="https://cointelegraph.com/news/nobody-is-holding-them-back-north-korean-cyber-attack-threat-rises">Cointelegraph</a></p><p style="font-weight: 400;">—</p><p style="font-weight: 400;"><u>unwire.hk </u>Mewe 專頁 : <a href="https://mewe.com/p/unwirehk"><u>https://mewe.com/p/unwirehk</u></a></p><h2> 最新影片</h2><iframe style="display: block; margin: 0px auto;" id="_ytid_84661" width="590" height="332" data-origwidth="590" data-origheight="332" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/?enablejsapi=1&amp;list=PLiEPZioiGtHw9_9gm4Ty0_pTEviOKNvfl&amp;autoplay=0&amp;cc_load_policy=0&amp;cc_lang_pref=&amp;iv_load_policy=1&amp;loop=0&amp;modestbranding=1&amp;rel=0&amp;fs=1&amp;playsinline=1&amp;autohide=1&amp;theme=light&amp;color=white&amp;controls=0&amp;" class="__youtube_prefs__  epyt-is-override  no-lazyload" title="YouTube player" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture" allowfullscreen="" data-no-lazy="1" data-skipgform_ajax_framebjll=""></iframe></p><div class="feedflare">
